lab 1:
Text analyzer.

The input is text data. Necessary count and output: how many times each word is repeated in the specified text average
number of words in a sentence median number of words in a sentence top-K most frequently repeated letter N-grams
(K and N have default values of 10 and 4, but it should be possible to set them from the keyboard).
For the solution, use the container dict () or its analogues and built-in operations on strings.
Provide for punctuation marks.

lab 3:
Django Web Application: E-commerce

Main tasks:
 • Implement CRUD (create, read, update, delete) operations;
 • Add all models to the admin panel. Display related models on one page;
 • Implement authorization/authentication mechanisms;
 • Add logging;
 • Add tests;
